messages.text: Do you know what time it is?
Something went wrong. I didn’t mean to do it. I swear man. I didn’t mean it.
Wait what? What happened? What went wrong?
I’m not laughing. I’ll show you.
Holy shit! What is that? Who is that? What did you do?
It was an accident. You gotta help me.
You have to call the cops. Holy shit Ian.
I can’t call the cops. I don’t want to go to jail. Please Jay. You’re the only one I can turn to.
Oh man, oh man, oh man. Where are you? I’ll come get you.
Shit I think I hear something
Tell me where you are Ian.
Oh man, oh man. Ian what the hell man. What’s going on?
I don’t think we should be texting this.
Okay, now he’s dead for sure
What the hell man? Who is that?
I’m at the old toy factory on the edge of town. Hurry up and come man.
Hey I’m here. Where are you?
I swear if you’re playing a prank on me I’m going to kick your ass.
If this was a prank where would I get the body???
I can’t believe you do this. I can’t believe I’m helping.
Good friends help you move the sofa. Best friends help you move the body.
We need to cover our tracks. I’ve been watching a lot of the ID channel.
I knew having you as a friend would come in handy.
Yeah well don’t make a habit of this.
Where the hell are you anyway?
Dead people tend to do that.
You haven’t told me who the body is.
It’s crazy dark up here too.
I don’t have any friends who would help me bury two bodies.
I’m not your friend anymore after this FYI
Don’t say that. I got you an early Bday gift and everything.
Beside you have to be my friend now and forever.
A little law called accessory after the fact.
Stop hiding and come out already.
What if they check our phone records?
I’m going to sing like a carney.
Shit I just stepped in something.
Sigh. Don’t throw up at my crime scene idiot.
Dur. That’s why you’re here. Were we not having the same conversation all this time?
Oh man, oh man. It’s blood.
Oh man. What are we going to do? What are going to do?
This is sick man. Just come out. Where are you?
Please Ian. What is this? What are you thinking?
I told you I need help. You came to help me didn’t you.
Don’t worry. It’ll all make sense in the end.
This is the most F’ed up thing you ever done man.
You’ll forgive me. You always do.
You’re still going to be my best friend right?
We’re going to be friends forever.
I don’t know. It’s too dark.
Who is this? Who the hell are you?
We use to play together all the time.
Growing up we lived next door to each other.
You said we would be friend forever.
You said that no one could ever replace me.
Then he came. And he took you from me. But we don’t have to worry about Ian anymore do we.
Skylar? We are still friends. We’re best friends.
So you’ll help me bury him?
Even though you were his friend.
I’m happy Jason. I’m so happy. We can be friends again.
Why don’t you come out? So I can see you.
I can see you just fine.
Don’t look for me Jason. You won’t find me.
I wish this would have worked out better. I wish I believed you.
Come on man. I want to be your friend. I want to be your friend.
I know you do. But it’s too late.
